Cid Raines (FFXIII)
Weapon type: Fist
Crystal Color: Black
Spheres: A A E

Skill 1: Offensive Shift
 Dispels own [Recovery Shift].
 Grants [Offensive Shift] to self for 6 turns.
 Raises own BRV based on Max BRV (30%).
 BRV Attack, BRV Attack+ become Mortal Crush while [Offensive Shift] is active.
 HP Attack, HP Attack+ become Ruinga while [Offensive Shift] is active.
 Uses: 3
15cp: Cid's Gloves
 +Extends base duration of [Offensive Shift] by 2 turns
 +Nullifies Action Delay
 +Improves BRV gain based on Max BRV (+10%)
  When using Mortal Crush:
 +Increases BRV potency
  When using Ruinga:
 +Increases BRV potency
 +Increases BRV damage dealt when attacking a single target (60%)
c.55: Offensive Shift Extend
 +Adds 2 uses
 +Improves BRV gain based on Max BRV (+20%)
 +Triggers a 3-hit Melee BRV+HP attack after use
 +Allows for 120% Gained BRV overflow
 +Allows for 150% Stolen BRV overflow
  When Using Mortal Crush:
 +Greatly increases BRV potency
 +Deals HP damage after BRV hits
 +Allows for 120% Stolen BRV overflow
 +Grants BRV to self based on HP damage dealt (30%)
  When using Ruinga:
 +Becomes a 3-hit AoE Magic BRV+ST HP attack
 +Deals 50% HP damage to non-targets
 +Greatly increases BRV potency
 +Allows for 120% Stolen BRV overflow

[Offensive Shift]: ATK Up (50%), Max BRV Up (40%)
                   BRV Regen (80% iBRV)
                   Stolen BRV Overflow Limit Up (30%)
Mortal Crush: 5-hit Melee BRV Attack.
              Instantly inflicts BREAK on all enemies when BREAKING main target
               *Does not affect enemies that are already BROKEN
Ruinga: 1-hit AoE Magic BRV+ST HP attack.
        Instantly inflicts BREAK on all enemies when BREAKING any target
         *Does not affect enemies that are already BROKEN

Skill 2: Recovery Shift
 Dispels own [Offensive Shift].
 Grants [Recovery Shift] to self for 6 turns.
 Raises own BRV based on INT BRV (100%).
 BRV Attack, BRV Attack+ become Cure while [Recovery Shift] is active.
 HP Attack, HP Attack+ become Ruin while [Recovery Shift] is active.
 Uses: 3
35cp: Godhand
 +Extends base duration of [Recovery Shift] by 2 turns
 +Nullifies Action Delay
 +Improves BRV gain based on INT BRV (+50%)
 +Restores HP to self (10% max HP)
  When using Cure:
 +Increases BRV gained from excess HP recovery (+100%)
 +Reduces Action Delay
  When using Ruin:
 +Increases BRV gain based on INT BRV (50%)
 +Increases BRV potency
 +Restores HP to party based on HP damage dealt (20%, 15% max HP cap)
c.60: Recovery Shift Extend
 +Adds 2 uses
 +Improves BRV gain based on INT BRV (+150%)
 +Multiplies own BRV by 1.3 before a 2-hit Magic BRV+HP attack
 +Allows for 120% Gained BRV overflow
 +Allows for 150% Stolen BRV overflow
  When Using Cure:
 +Extends effects to party
 +Improves HP recovery based on INT BRV (40%)
 +Raises HP recovery limit (+10%)
  When using Ruin:
 +Increases BRV gain based on INT BRV (+100%)
 +Greatly increases BRV potency
 +Allows for 120% Gained BRV overflow
 +Allows for 120% Stolen BRV overflow
 +Grants BRV to party based on HP damage dealt (20%)
 
[Recovery Shift]: DEF Up (80%), INT BRV Up (60%), Max BRV Up (40%)
                  HP Regen (15% max HP)
                  Gained BRV Overflow Limit Up (30%)
Cure: Restores HP to party based on own INT BRV (60%, 20% Max HP cap)
      Excess HP recovered is converted to BRV Gain (100%)
Ruin: Gain BRV based on INT BRV (150%), followed by a 2-hit Magic BRV+HP attack.
      Instantly inflicts BREAK on all enemies when BREAKING main target
       *Does not affect enemies that are already BROKEN
 
EX: Seraphim Claw
 +Equips EX ability Seraphic Ray
4-hit AoE Magic BRV+HP attack.
Deals 100% HP damage to all targets.
Removes all buffs from targets.
Instantly inflicts BREAK on all enemies when BREAKING any target
 *Does not affect enemies that are already BROKEN
 Recast: Slightly Slow
  -LB1: Increases BRV damage dealt by 10%
  -LB2: Increases recast speed of Seraphic Ray by 20%
  -LB3: Grants [Will to Fight Fate] to self for 4 turns upon use
 EX+: Increases BRV potency
      Allows for 120% Stolen BRV overflow
      BRV Attack becomes BRV Attack+ while [Offensive Shift] and [Recovery Shift] are not active
      HP Attack becomes HP Attack+ while [Offensive Shift] and [Recovery Shift] are not active
  -LB1: Increases own ATK (40%) and Max BRV (40%)
        Extends duration of all self buffs by 2 turns after use
  -LB2: At Quest start:
        Grants [Will to Fight Fate] to self for 6 turns
        For the first turn:
        -Does not consume ability uses
        -No Action Delay
        -Does not increase turn count
        -Decreases Friend Support and Summon action count
  -LB3: Gain BRV based on INT BRV (120%) before a 6-hit AoE Magic BRV+HP attack.
        Allows for 120% Stolen BRV overflow.
        Allows for 120% Gained BRV overflow.

[Will to Fight Fate]: ATK Up (50%), Max BRV Up (30%)
                      Increases BRV damage dealt to BROKEN targets (50%)
BRV Attack+: 3-hit Melee BRV attack.
             Instantly inflicts BREAK on all enemies when BREAKING main target
              *Does not affect enemies that are already BROKEN
HP Attack+: 2-hit Melee BRV+HP attack.
            Instantly inflicts BREAK on all enemies when BREAKING main target
             *Does not affect enemies that are already BROKEN

LD: Oversoul
 +Equips LD ability Metamorphose
Completely recovers own HP.
Grants BRV to self based on Max BRV (100%).
Grants special effect [Metamorphosis] to self for 3 turns.
8-hit AoE Magic BRV+HP attack.
HP damage dealt is split evenly.
Allows for 180% Stolen BRV overflow.
Allows for 120% Gained BRV overflow.
Instantly inflicts BREAK on all enemies when BREAKING any target
 *Does not affect enemies that are already BROKEN
 Uses: 3
  -LB1: Raises own ATK (20%)
        Increases BRV damage dealt by 10%
  -LB2: Raises own ATK (20%)
        Extends base duration of [Metamorphosis] by 3 turns
  -LB3: Raises own ATK (20%)
        Adds 1 use
Board Passive: LD Extend
 +Increases BRV gain based on Max BRV (+100%)
 +Triggers an AoE HP attack after BRV gain (but before BRV attacks)
 +HP damage dealt is split evenly
 
[Metamorphosis]: ATK Up (60%), INT BRV Up (50%), Max BRV Up (40%)
                 BRV Damage Reduction (20%)
                 If BRV is less than INT BRV at turn start, recovers BRV back to INT BRV
